== Purpose <purpose>

Public festivals and theatrical performances were central to civic life in many ancient cultures. These gatherings celebrated gods, heroes, and the identity of the city itself. Beyond entertainment, such events reinforced shared values and strengthened the cohesion of the population.

The Theatre allows your city to host grand cultural festivals that inspire its citizens and expand its cultural influence.

Once built, the Theatre unlocks a festival event that can be performed periodically. Each festival consumes resources but grants culture points, helping your civilization expand and progress culturally.

